'''Hannelore Knuts''' (born 4 November 1977) is a [[Belgium|Belgian]] actress and fashion [[model (person)|model]]. She has appeared on the cover of ''[[Vogue (magazine)|Vogue]]'' seven times: five times on the [[Vogue Italia|Italian edition]], and once each on the South Korean and Japanese editions.<ref name=fmd/> Her 2011-12 film credits include [[Nicolas Provost]]'s ''[[The Invader (2011 film)|The Invader]]''<ref>[http://www.nicolasprovost.com/films/482/ ''The Invader''] on Nicolas Provost's website.</ref> and the [[Radio Soulwax]] project ''Dave'', in which she plays the title role of [[David Bowie]].

